00:40:01,232 --> 00:40:02,934
The whole room is a mess.

769
00:40:03,068 --> 00:40:04,970
Ah, I just can't
believe it. Okay.

770
00:40:05,103 --> 00:40:08,406
I could use a salami on rye,
and a lot of nuts
with cream soda.

771
00:40:08,540 --> 00:40:09,875
Maybe the Jap
wants some sushi.

