00:40:10,008 --> 00:40:10,942
Who's the Jap?

773
00:40:11,076 --> 00:40:12,410
Uh, it's Yakimoto Yakimura.

774
00:40:12,544 --> 00:40:15,113
Yeah, hi, yeah, this is,
um, it's, uh, room 619, yeah.

775
00:40:15,246 --> 00:40:18,450
I need a salami on rye,
I need a cream soda,
and, uh, two coffees.

776
00:40:18,584 --> 00:40:19,951
And there's a lot
of carts up here

777
00:40:20,085 --> 00:40:22,387
that need to be taken away.
So could you hurry?

778
00:40:22,521 --> 00:40:26,925
FRANCOISE:
Nancy, I, I want some, uh,
ice cream and chocolate sauce.

779
00:40:27,058 --> 00:40:28,359
How do you say it?

780
00:40:28,494 --> 00:40:30,395
NANCY:
Yeah, a hot fudge sundae?
Yeah, thank you.

781
00:40:30,529 --> 00:40:31,930
NANCY: Yeah, could you
add to that a hot
fudge sundae

782
00:40:32,063 --> 00:40:33,932
with vanilla ice cream,
and please hurry.

783
00:40:34,065 --> 00:40:35,567
Thank you. Bye.
